{
  "stem": "1496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a uniform factory, a shoe factory, woodworking factory, all kinds of shops, but-- metal shop-- all the work had to be done for the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most of the people stayed in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However, there were some people which had the special permit to go out from the ghetto to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was one of them who had the permit, because the factory I worked was outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I had to leave every morning and come back in the evening, after work, come back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Also, once in awhile, the Nazis-- quite often, actually-- the Nazis used to come in with trucks and take people out to perform all kind of work for the-- in the barracks and so forth for the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was by myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to show my permit, and I was going out from the ghetto by myself and coming by myself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were a few people that had this kind of situation permits to leave the ghetto and come back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For me, it was quite an advantage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because number one, I still have contact with some non-Jewish people, and having contact once in a while, I was smuggling some food into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was a very risky operation, because we were checked on the gate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Luckily, they never caught me smuggling in, because if I would be caught, I wouldn't be here to tell you this story, because most time, people were executed right at the gate.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So actually, by having the opportunity to smuggle, I had helped my parents and my brothers to have a little extra food besides the rations.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was an advantage to be having even contact with non-Jewish people, being on the outside.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
